heading: Looking for love in all the wrong places?
description:
Single professional, well educated man in good shape who has lacked affection for a long time. I'd like to catch up.  I live alone as my children are grown and have moved to other states to pursue their careers. My family, my 2 dogs, ancestry (I'm an 11th generation Southerner), the Crimson Tide, any fast Porsche, history, literature, writing, travels to Europe, and romance are some of my passions. Should you lean to the intellectual side, know that my life has been unique; think of me relating to you like Sterne's Tristram Shandy, only rather than an English gentleman's life, my story would be more similar to the Southern Gothic writings of Flannery O'Connor. I can promise to keep you entertained.



I've been described by others as intelligent, loyal, sarcastic, witty, funny, serious, silly, conceited, self-deprecating, aggressive, occasionally humble, arrogant, nice, sensitive, talented, and fun. Which of these traits I display could well depend on you. Should you deign to meet me, I promise to make you laugh. Your laughter may be with me or at my expense, but my life has bordered on the unbelievable at times and therein lies humor.



I could write much more but I'll refrain yet leave you with one final thought: for 32 consecutive years I have vacationed in the summer for a week with my two sisters and our collective seven children. I believe this reveals something important about me.



Well, one more thought: I need to be discreet and have pictures I can show you so you'll know what I look like. You can see a few on this site by making a request to see my hidden pictures. If those 4 or 5 pictures are not sufficient, just send me your email address or number to text other pictures to you.



DO NOT ASK ME FOR MONEY BEFORE YOU MEET ME IN PERSON. THE ANSWER IS NO. I CANNOT SAVE ALL THE SINGLE MOTHERS OUT THERE. IF YOU NEED MONEY AFTER JUST TALKING TO ME OR TEXTING ME ON THE PHONE AND NOT MEETING ME IN PERSON, GO ELSEWHERE. I'M A SOFT TOUCH AND I AM SYMPATHETIC TO OTHERS, BUT FRANKLY, I'M TIRED OF ALL THE STORIES OF MISFORTUNE. FINALLY, IF YOU LIVE FAR AWAY PLEASE DO NOT MESSAGE ME. I CANNOT MAKE LONG DISTANCE ROMANCES WORK.
describe_seeking:
I'm looking for an attractive and intelligent woman who likes great food, great hotels, great travel locations, and great conversation. Sometimes I would just like company for a home cooked meal and an evening spent watching a movie. I'd like to make a new friend or even more. I'm something of a romantic at heart, so I'm not on this site for just a good time. I want more. I'm not saying you have to marry me or love me, but I would like to at least make a special friend. If you seek a relationship with a financial arrangement, we can discuss that. 



To date me you don't have to be a Phi Beta Kappa college graduate like I am, but I prefer women who can discuss more than nail polish, shoes, and your hair. OK, well, I am all about hair (I was voted Best Boy's Hair in the 8th grade…all downhill from there) so we can discuss that. But I'm not a superficial guy. I'd like to get to know you. Again, I'm not on here just looking for a good time. The women are pretty on this site so I thought I'd try it. But if you think it humorous to stand a man up (this happens to me often with young women on this site) please quit wasting my time, grow up, go elsewhere, and find younger men.
